{"tid":1703084,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"11.11想成功，請做定推演，想參與又唔知點參與既人，請入黎討論","createTime":"2019-11-10T06:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T08:13:55.000Z","uid":161430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4249d09fd28929b9628569ce24f2d52c36c9a000","tid":1703084,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"一，好多人想參與但根本唔知點做好，例如邊度集合，好在搵左陣終於搵到人講，請分享比更多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">11.11 朝早 5點 會公佈集合位置聚人<br />\n請密切留意channel</span><br />\n夠人先做到野<br />\n單拖手足可以埋伏喺附近餐廳/m記<br />\n扮等巴士都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">活動冇詳情又朝早搞，好易令想出去特別單拖既冇頭緒點join, 最後就好散，冇人。</span>好在暫時叫有以上資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁請留意5點公佈喇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二，對家唔係傻，聽朝各黨鐵站一定會有狗車捕定，擺曬人喺度，<span style=\"color: orange;\">今日大家好上定連登，用定一日時間推演遇到各種情況時點算好</span>，唔好到時發現搞唔掂，跟住失鳩敗先上黎發悔氣喇，第五個月喇請事前推演。<br />\n<br />\n三，祝成功"},{"pid":"ccb0b33dd932ec51368582654367b45a25c66479","tid":1703084,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母</span><br />\n<br />\n【黎明行動】<br />\n雙十一．周圍塞<br />\n<br />\n頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=e95ca015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br />\n<br />\n公海: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=ad0e60b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好阻人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e5b9c88f25c9acf73f3ee997829fc2778c30e7","tid":1703084,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"